<ab facs="#facs_64_r1l3">etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅch <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ wır <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> eyten = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_64_r1l4"><expan>holcʒ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> beſant vnd ſein red <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> gehöret wolten <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſo ıſt er noch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_64_r1l5">niht anheim bey vns . Vnd ıſt auch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> wıſſens ſeıd derʒeıt als Jr vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_64_r1l6">nehſt ſchrybt . niht bey vns <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / Nu wıſſen wır für Jn darcʒu nıht ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_64_r1l7"><expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> als Jr ſelbs wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteen</expan> mugt / VVenn er <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> herheim kombt ſo <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
