<ab facs="#facs_64_r1l9"><expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> / Denn wo wır eẅch lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>vıgı<ex>lia</ex></expan> <expan>ſymo<ex>n</ex>ıs</expan> et Jude </ab>
